The '''[[2007-08 NCAA Division I men's basketball season|2007-08]] [[Ball State Cardinals men's basketball]] team''' is a NCAA Division I [[college basketball]] team competing in the [[Mid-American Conference]].
==Preseason== Billy Taylor replaced Ronny Thompson as head coach of the team. Only Peyton Stovall, Brandon Lampley, Anthony Newell and Rashaun McLemore (who redshirted) would return from last year's team.
==Awards== ===Mid-American Conference Player of the Week=== * Peyton Stovall, January 7
